Master Independent Contractor Services Agreement (MICSA) 

This Master Independent Contractor Services Agreement ("Agreement") is made as of ____________ (the "Effective Date"), by and between VanMobile Services "Principle" and "Contractor").
Individually or collectively, VanMobile and Contractor may be referred to herein as a "party" or the "parties." Any capitalized term used herein shall have the meaning given to it in the attached Standard Terms and Conditions. 
The terms and conditions of this Agreement will apply to each business transaction between the parties for the provision of Services for VanMobile by Contractor. 
By signing below, the parties agree to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, including without limitation the Standard Terms and Conditions attached hereto and all exhibits thereto.
This Agreement may be executed in counterparts, each of which will be considered an original, but all of which together will constitute the same instrument.
Once signed, any reproduction of this Agreement, or any attachment or exhibit hereto, made by reliable means (for example, photocopy, PDF, digital copy, or facsimile) is considered an original and all Services ordered under this Agreement will be subject to it. 


