j) any other confidential information concerning the business of VanMobile, their manners of operation, or other confidential data of any kind, nature, or description. 

6.2 Non-Disclosure Agreement. In connection with the performance of Services by Contractor to VanMobile ("Performance of Services"), the Contractor acknowledges that the Contractor will have access to Confidential Information and that VanMobile: 
