f) "Effective Date" has the meaning set forth in the preamble. 

g) "VanMobile" has the meaning set forth in the preamble. 

h) "VanMobile Materials" means all materials and information, including documents, data, knowÂ­how, ideas, methodologies, specifications, software, content and technology, in any form or media, directly or indirectly provided or made available to Contractor by or on behalf of VanMobile in connection with this Agreement, whether or not the same: (a) are owned by VanMobile, a Third Party or in the public domain; or (b) qualify for or are protected by any Intellectual Property Rights. 

